description:
*New Age to Christ: Leah's Testimony* | On this episode of LED Live, we have a special guest, Leah, who is sharing her powerful testimony about her experience in the New Age Movement. Leah tried Kundalini meditation to overcome anxiety, and it WORKED! She began communicating with spirit guides and angels and was such an advocate for the practice that she started a YouTube Channel called 'Leah For The Light' to promote the New Age...that is until God opened her eyes to the truth. @leahforthelight8201
